---

<Base title="Partial Hospitalization (PHP) in CT | Hopewell Health Solutions" description="Partial hospitalization (PHP) at Hopewell Health Solutions, Glastonbury CT — 6 structured hours a day for depression, anxiety, trauma & co-occurring disorders. Most insurance accepted.">
  <Header />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-crema">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 pt-8 pb-16">
      <nav class="text-xs text-muted mb-6"><a href="/" class="hover:text-azul">Home</a> / <a href="/#programs" class="hover:text-azul">Programs</a> / <span class="text-ink">PHP</span></nav>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_390px] gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">Recovery within reach · Partial Hospitalization Program · Glastonbury, CT</p>
          <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-ink leading-[1.08]">Partial Hospitalization Program (PHP) in Connecticut</h1>
          <div class="mt-5 h-px w-16 bg-gold"></div>
          <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm">
            <span class="text-yellow-400 text-base leading-none">★★★★★</span>
            <span class="font-semibold text-ink">4.8</span>
            <span class="text-muted">· 368 Google reviews</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            {heroUsps.map((u) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3 text-ink"><span class="grid h-7 w-7 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-azul-light text-azul"><Icon name={u.icon} class="h-4 w-4" /></span><span class="leading-snug pt-0.5">{u.t}</span></li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="tel:8607351448" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-lg border border-azul px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-azul hover:bg-azul-light transition"><Icon name="phone" class="h-5 w-5" />(860) 735-1448</a>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-muted">Medically reviewed by Katrin Moskowitz, DNP, PMHNP-BC</p>
        </div>
        <div id="verify" class="lg:sticky lg:top-28 scroll-mt-28"><LeadForm /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <MediaStrip bg="white" heading="Our clinicians, featured across Connecticut" />

  <!-- WHAT IS (image left / text right) -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <img src="/Assets/AdobeStock_403830351.webp" alt="Partial hospitalization day program in Glastonbury, CT" loading="lazy" class="rounded-2xl w-full h-72 lg:h-96 object-cover" />
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">A higher level of care, without an overnight stay</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">What is a Partial Hospitalization Program?</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-azul/40"></div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[17px]">Hopewell Health Solutions’ Partial Hospitalization Program (PHP) provides concierge, customized, comprehensive, structured treatment for several hours daily. It’s an ideal model for those needing more support than outpatient therapy, but not requiring inpatient hospitalization.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[17px]">PHP lets you live at home while receiving intensive group therapy, individual therapy, medication management, skill-building, and experiential wellness — including yoga, art therapy, sound healing, weight training, hiking, Reiki, needlework, and meditation.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">Want the full breakdown? Read our guide: <a href="/blog/what-is-a-partial-hospitalization-program-php/" class="text-azul font-semibold">What is a Partial Hospitalization Program (PHP)?</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BENEFITS (text left / image right) -->
  <section class="bg-crema">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <div class="lg:order-2"><img src="/Assets/AdobeStock_542909901.webp" alt="A supportive partial hospitalization group at Hopewell Health Solutions" loading="lazy" class="rounded-2xl w-full h-72 lg:h-96 object-cover" /></div>
      <div class="lg:order-1">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">A comprehensive approach</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">The benefits of PHP</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-azul/40"></div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[17px]">PHP is beneficial for:</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2.5">
          {benefitsFor.map((b) => <li class="flex gap-3 text-ink"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-azul"></span><span class="leading-snug">{b}</span></li>)}
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[17px]">This goal-oriented program focuses on <strong>rapid stabilization, enhancing coping skills, and improving overall quality of life.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SPECIALIZED TREATMENT + MULTIMODAL APPROACH -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">Specialized treatment &amp; interventions</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">A multimodal treatment approach</h2>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-4 h-px w-16 bg-azul/40"></div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[17px]">Hopewell Health Solutions’ PHP offers <strong>6 structured hours of treatment daily, 5–6 days a week.</strong> Through evidence-based modalities, individualized plans, and specialized interventions, our PHP stabilizes symptoms of substance use and co-occurring disorders — while promoting successful community reintegration and long-term recovery. A unique feature: a customizable approach that lets you build a tailored schedule for the group component of PHP.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {approach.map((a) => (
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-line bg-crema p-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-azul-light text-azul"><Icon name={a.icon} class="h-6 w-6" /></span><h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink leading-tight">{a.t}</h3></div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-ink leading-relaxed text-[15px]">{a.d}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHP SCHEDULE -->
  <section class="bg-crema">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">The structure is the medicine</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">A day in PHP</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Monday–Friday · held at our Glastonbury location, with offices in West Hartford, East Hampton &amp; Westbrook.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-10 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-line bg-white divide-y divide-line">
        {phpDay.map(([time, act]) => (
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-36 text-sm font-semibold text-azul">{time}</span>
            <span class="text-ink leading-snug">{act}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHP vs IOP (comparison band) -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5 py-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">Find the right starting point</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">PHP vs. IOP — what’s the difference?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">The difference comes down to intensity. Many clients step down from PHP into our <a href="/programs/adult-mental-health-iop/" class="text-azul font-semibold hover:text-azul-dark transition">Adult IOP</a> as they stabilize — Hopewell Health Solutions helps you find the right level.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 items-stretch">
        <div class="flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white border border-azul/30">
          <img src="/Assets/full%20team%20happy.webp" alt="Partial hospitalization — the highest level of outpatient care" loading="lazy" class="h-48 w-full shrink-0 object-cover" />
          <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col p-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-azul-light text-azul"><Icon name="calendar" class="h-6 w-6" /></span><h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">PHP</h3></div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-ink leading-relaxed">About <strong>six hours a day, 5–6 days a week</strong> — the highest level of outpatient care. Best for stabilizing after a crisis or stepping down from inpatient.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white border border-azul/30">
          <img src="/Assets/couple%20hugging.webp" alt="Intensive outpatient — care that fits around your life" loading="lazy" class="h-48 w-full shrink-0 object-cover" />
          <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col p-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-sage-light text-sage"><Icon name="refresh" class="h-6 w-6" /></span><h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">IOP</h3></div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-ink leading-relaxed">About <strong>three hours a day, four days a week</strong> — lighter structure so you can keep working, studying, or caring for family.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S DESIGNED FOR (text left / image right) -->
  <section class="bg-crema">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <div class="lg:order-2"><img src="/Assets/Guy%20facing%20the%20horizon.webp" alt="Adult considering partial hospitalization in Connecticut" loading="lazy" class="rounded-2xl w-full h-72 lg:h-96 object-cover" /></div>
      <div class="lg:order-1">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-azul">Support tailored to you</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink">Who our PHP is designed for</h2>
